      // falsely freeze the keyboard until a teleport / CancelWalk fired,
      // making movement only possible via map-click (which goes through
      // AutoWalkPacket and bypasses the freeze). Reproduced 2026-05-01.
      // Cleared on CREATURE_TELEPORT, CANCEL_WALK, or auto-timeout.
      //
      // Two-gate check: NotPathable DAT flag AND a `floorchange` property
