// Sticky-direction streaming walk. WALK_START tells the server "I'm
// holding this direction" — server walks the player on its own clock
// until WALK_STOP. Eliminates the round-trip-per-tile cost that hurts
// keyboard movement on bad-CF nodes. Easy revert: delete BEGIN/END
// blocks here + in keyboard.js + server-side movement handler + the
// constants.json opcodes WALK_START/WALK_STOP.

